---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="PHCDevworks"
  description="Design systems, UI tooling, and developer infrastructure. Open source. Built for developers."
>
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] w-full">
      <h1
        class="text-[clamp(3rem,15vw,12rem)] font-black leading-[0.9] mb-8 sm:mb-12 lg:mb-16 tracking-[-0.04em] break-words lg:whitespace-nowrap"
      >
        PHCDEV<span class="text-[#ff0055]">WORKS</span>
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-[clamp(1.5rem,5vw,4rem)] font-black leading-[1.1] mb-6 sm:mb-8 lg:mb-12 tracking-[-0.02em]"
      >
        We build design systems, UI tooling, and developer infrastructure.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[clamp(1.125rem,2vw,1.75rem)] leading-normal opacity-70">
        Everything is open source. Everything is on GitHub.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-24 sm:mb-32 lg:mb-48 px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
    <h2
      class="text-[clamp(2.5rem,8vw,6rem)] font-black mb-12 sm:mb-16 lg:mb-24 tracking-[-0.03em]"
    >
      PROJECTS
    </h2>

    <div class="grid gap-10 sm:gap-16 lg:gap-20">
      <div class="border-l-4 border-[#ff0055] pl-4 sm:pl-6 lg:pl-8">
        <h3
          class="text-[clamp(1.75rem,5vw,3.5rem)] font-black mb-4 tracking-[-0.02em]"
        >
          <a
            href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-tokens"
            class="text-[#ff0055] no-underline border-b-4 border-[#ff0055] break-all"
          >
            SPECTRE TOKENS
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[clamp(1.25rem,2vw,1.5rem)] leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          Core design primitives for the Spectre suite. Colors, spacing,
          typography, radii, shadows. Outputs to CSS variables, JS/TS objects,
          and theme presets for WordPress, Astro, 11ty.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-[#ff0055] pl-4 sm:pl-6 lg:pl-8">
        <h3
          class="text-[clamp(1.75rem,5vw,3.5rem)] font-black mb-4 tracking-[-0.02em]"
        >
          <a
            href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-ui"
            class="text-[#ff0055] no-underline border-b-4 border-[#ff0055] break-all"
          >
            SPECTRE UI
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[clamp(1.25rem,2vw,1.5rem)] leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          Cross-platform UI built on Spectre Tokens. Tailwind-powered design
          system delivering consistent CSS utilities, component classes, and
          design recipes for WordPress, Astro, 11ty.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-[#ff0055] pl-4 sm:pl-6 lg:pl-8">
        <h3
          class="text-[clamp(1.75rem,5vw,3.5rem)] font-black mb-4 tracking-[-0.02em]"
        >
          <a
            href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-ui-astro"
            class="text-[#ff0055] no-underline border-b-4 border-[#ff0055] break-all"
          >
            SPECTRE UI ASTRO
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[clamp(1.25rem,2vw,1.5rem)] leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          First-class Astro layer for Spectre UI. Typed, SSR-friendly components
          (Button, Card, Input) that wrap Spectre UI classes and tokens. Native
          Astro, zero bloat.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-[#ff0055] pl-4 sm:pl-6 lg:pl-8">
        <h3
          class="text-[clamp(1.75rem,5vw,3.5rem)] font-black mb-4 tracking-[-0.02em]"
        >
          <a
            href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-icons"
            class="text-[#ff0055] no-underline border-b-4 border-[#ff0055] break-all"
          >
            SPECTRE ICONS
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[clamp(1.25rem,2vw,1.5rem)] leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          Modern SVG icon sets for WordPress builders. Lucide, Font Awesome, and
          more. Unified manager, performance-first. Replaces dozens of separate
          icon plugins.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-24 sm:mb-32 lg:mb-48 px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
    <h2
      class="text-[clamp(2.5rem,8vw,6rem)] font-black mb-12 sm:mb-16 lg:mb-24 tracking-[-0.03em]"
    >
      PHILOSOPHY
    </h2>
    <div class="grid gap-8 sm:gap-12 lg:gap-16">
      <p
        class="text-[clamp(1.5rem,4vw,3rem)] font-black leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em]"
      >
        Design tokens once. <span class="text-[#ff0055]">Use everywhere.</span>
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-[clamp(1.5rem,4vw,3rem)] font-black leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em]"
      >
        Tokens feed CSS. <span class="text-[#ff0055]">
          CSS feeds components.</span
        >
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-[clamp(1.5rem,4vw,3rem)] font-black leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em]"
      >
        <span class="text-[#ff0055]">Open source.</span> No vendor lock.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-[clamp(1.5rem,4vw,3rem)] font-black leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em]"
      >
        Build what you need. <span class="text-[#ff0055]">
          Modify what you want.</span
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16 sm:mb-24 lg:mb-32 px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
    <h2
      class="text-[clamp(2.5rem,8vw,6rem)] font-black mb-6 sm:mb-8 lg:mb-12 tracking-[-0.03em]"
    >
      LINKS
    </h2>
    <p
      class="text-[clamp(1.5rem,4vw,2.5rem)] font-black mb-4 sm:mb-6 lg:mb-8 tracking-[-0.02em]"
    >
      <a
        href="https://github.com/phcdevworks"
        class="text-[#ff0055] no-underline border-b-4 border-[#ff0055] break-all"
      >
        github.com/phcdevworks
      </a>
    </p>
    <p class="text-[clamp(1.125rem,1.5vw,1.25rem)] opacity-70">
      All repos. All docs. All roadmaps.
    </p>
  </section>

  <footer class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-16 px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
    <p class="text-sm opacity-50">Â© 2025 PHCDevworks</p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
